  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden Felines: Japanese Village  is a short yet relaxing hidden object game set in Japan. Explore beautifully hand-drawn isometric art as you search for 100 cats who are waiting to be found.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Camera Movement </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >w,a,s,d and arrow keys</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left click hold and middle mouse button drag</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Edge panning </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hint System</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features a hint system with camera panning. When activated, the camera dynamically pans to reveal the location of a hidden cat somewhere within its view.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden Felines: Japanese Village  is a short yet relaxing hidden object game set in Japan. Explore beautifully hand-drawn isometric art as you search for 100 cats who are waiting to be found.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Camera Movement </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >w,a,s,d and arrow keys</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left click hold and middle mouse button drag</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Edge panning </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hint System</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features a hint system with camera panning. When activated, the camera dynamically pans to reveal the location of a hidden cat somewhere within its view.</p></li></ul>",
